name: on my stage
description:
made on 2018. back then, i'm very insecure and depressed. so i made this artowk to remind me to believe in myself. now, finally that feelings no longer inside me. i'm happy now. i'm proud of myself because i can get out of that situation safe and sound. in fact, i'm thankful for those bad years. i'm stronger now.
